187
00:10:56,404 --> 00:10:57,824
Momka iz Cikaga.

188
00:11:01,434 --> 00:11:04,000
Misliš da je mrtav ili znaš da jeste?

189
00:11:04,092 --> 00:11:06,321
Tako i ja mislim.

190
00:11:07,872 --> 00:11:08,723
Dobro.

191
00:11:09,409 --> 00:11:10,905
Hvala, cuvaj se.

192
00:11:12,676 --> 00:11:14,020
Misli da je mrtav.

193
00:11:15,176 --> 00:11:16,212
Nemoguce je.

194
00:11:16,231 --> 00:11:19,088
Ne koristimo više tu rec.

195
00:11:28,149 --> 00:11:28,923
Freddy.

196
00:11:29,782 --> 00:11:30,513
Ike.

197
00:11:31,543 --> 00:11:32,537
Slušaj...

198
00:11:33,177 --> 00:11:35,132
Secaš li se Bob Satterfield-a?

199
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:37,924
Da.

200
