201
00:11:43,813 --> 00:11:44,696
U redu.

202
00:11:44,773 --> 00:11:45,887
Hvala.

203
00:11:46,695 --> 00:11:48,497
Ne, dobro su. Hvala.

204
00:11:51,308 --> 00:11:54,497
Misli da je mrtav, ali nije siguran.

205
00:11:54,575 --> 00:11:55,646
