216
00:12:20,201 --> 00:12:21,621
Kao i Satterfield.

217
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:34,795
Zdravo, šampione.

218
00:12:34,871 --> 00:12:35,756
Hej, prijatelju.

219
00:12:35,832 --> 00:12:37,437
Hoceš nešto da jedeš?

220
00:12:39,676 --> 00:12:40,560
Kako si ti?

221
00:12:40,637 --> 00:12:43,749
